Preparations for the introduction of free pneumococcal vaccination are culminating.
The Pharmaceutical Institute already sets the maximum prices for vaccines that health insurance will pay.
Specialists also see clearly in the vaccination process.
A new vaccination.
Free vaccines for children in August.
